content: e m bartels n otes the symbol v is used to indicate a kfb knit in front and back not a slip_stitch it adds an extra stitch that in this pattern is removed in the next pattern row by an extra decrease don t worry if your stitch count does not match the number of stitches shown in the chart for row with the kfb stitch 9 copyright ©2023 denise e m bartels
